      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, complete with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical chassis maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the car retains its signature communicative handling. Recent valve adjustments and rod bearing inspections confirm the mechanical health of this high-performance icon.",
